Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: log2slack
Version: 0.3
Summary: Simple logger for posting log to slack.com
Home-page: https://github.com/rickmak/log2slack
Author: Rick Mak
Author-email: rick.mak@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: Example for Configuration file.
        
        Reference: https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.config.html#configuration-file-format
        
        ```
        [handler_slack]
        class = log2slack.SlackHandler
        args = ('domain.slack.com', 'slack_token', '#channel', 'display_name')
        level = ERROR
        formatter = generic
        ```
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
Requires: requests
